                                "info": "Ego is the Enemy by Ryan Holiday",
                                "book_cover":"/assets/images/bookpics/ego is the enemy.jpg",
                                "description": "“While the history books are filled with tales of obsessive visionary geniuses who remade the world in their image with sheer, almost irrational force, I’ve found that history is also made by individuals who fought their egos at every turn, who eschewed the spotlight, and who put their higher goals above their desire for recognition.” —from the prologue",
